98
00:09:43,374 --> 00:09:48,482
{\an7}<i>He got up... from a Sekizo</i>
<i>barrage?! </i>

99
00:10:13,916 --> 00:10:15,719
[gasping]

100
00:10:17,221 --> 00:10:20,826
{\an1}Where am I? Does this
mean...?

101
00:10:20,859 --> 00:10:22,494
