00:12:14,378 --> 00:12:18,216
{\an7}<i>sense greatly the</i>
<i>differences between myself</i>
<i>and the other.... </i>

132
00:12:18,250 --> 00:12:22,855
{\an7}<i>I was also able to</i>
<i>formalistically regulate and</i>
<i>learn new mores and words,</i>

133
00:12:22,889 --> 00:12:23,357
{\an8}<i>however- </i>

134
00:12:23,390 --> 00:12:25,659
{\an1}Shut up, already!

135
00:12:25,693 --> 00:12:29,031
{\an1}I don't have the time to
be sitting around and
listening to some weird

136
00:12:29,065 --> 00:12:30,633
{\an1}geezer prattle on, you
know?!

137
00:12:30,666 --> 00:12:34,738
{\an1}Not just searching for
words... But there also
remains some ambiguity in

138
00:12:34,771 --> 00:12:36,274
scholarship.

139
00:12:36,307 --> 00:12:40,313
{\an1}If communication of wills
can't be achieved in
addition to difficulty of

140
00:12:40,347 --> 00:12:41,381
definition...

141
00:12:41,414 --> 00:12:44,151
{\an1}I can see that I shall have
to speak simply...

142
00:12:44,185 --> 00:12:48,657
{\an1}...taking into account
current idealistic and
materialistic thinking.

143
00:12:48,690 --> 00:12:54,366
{\an1}Listen, are you an alien or
something? I mean, you do
seem super dignified but...

144
00:12:56,234 --> 00:13:00,907
{\an1}That's a bit much dontcha
think? An alien? Seriously?
[chuckling]

145
00:13:02,809 --> 00:13:04,212
Huh...?!

146
00:13:04,245 --> 00:13:08,317
{\an1}Well, maybe that ain't too
far off. Anyway...

147
00:13:08,817 --> 00:13:10,487
Hmm?

148
00:13:11,955 --> 00:13:13,791
{\an1}You still don't understand?

149
00:13:13,824 --> 00:13:16,695
{\an1}That conversation would pose
such a complex challenge...

150
00:13:16,728 --> 00:13:19,699
{\an1}No! No, no! That was fine
just now!

151
00:13:19,732 --> 00:13:26,207
{\an4}No, I finally get you! I was
just shocked 'cause your
speaking style changed so
much, ya know?

152
00:13:26,242 --> 00:13:30,447
{\an1}Oh, yeah, for real? Then
I'll keep going like this.
I'm much pleased!

153
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,314
Uh, yeah...

154
00:13:31,348 --> 00:13:32,417
[groaning]

155
00:13:34,752 --> 00:13:39,325
{\an1}Oh... uh... but those words
don't really match up with
your face at all, so it's

