00:13:39,359 --> 00:13:41,228
{\an1}kinda super-scary...

157
00:13:41,262 --> 00:13:44,299
{\an7}<i>And he loses all dignity</i>
<i>too... </i>

158
00:13:44,332 --> 00:13:48,204
{\an1}I guess... dial it back a
