164
00:14:05,127 --> 00:14:08,031
{\an1}Indeed. I'm getting the
hang of it, too.

165
00:14:08,064 --> 00:14:11,168
{\an1}Oh, man, finally, I can talk
with you!

166
00:14:11,202 --> 00:14:15,373
{\an1}So, anyway, who are you? And
if you know a lot about this
place, I want to know how to

167
