168
00:14:18,545 --> 00:14:20,647
{\an1}Don't ask everything all
at once!

169
00:14:20,681 --> 00:14:24,619
{\an1}I'm someone from the past,
someone who is already dead.

170
00:14:24,652 --> 00:14:29,092
{\an1}A monk wandering the world
as chakra, crossing
generations, ascertaining

171
00:14:29,126 --> 00:14:31,796
{\an1}the course of Ninshu, the
Ninja Creed.

172
00:14:31,829 --> 00:14:38,071
{\an4}My name's Hagoromo. I'm the
founder of Ninshu, the Ninja
Creed, known as the Sage of
Six Paths.

173
00:14:38,104 --> 00:14:40,207
{\an1}The Sage of Six Paths?!

174
00:14:40,241 --> 00:14:45,381
{\an1}You mean that you're the
sage that Nagato and Pervy
Sage told me about?! Really?!

175
00:14:45,647 --> 00:14:47,416
{\an1}Oh, so you know of me?

176
00:14:47,451 --> 00:14:51,855
{\an1}Yeah, of course I do!
You're the one who first
created Ninjutsu right?

177
00:14:51,889 --> 00:14:56,061
{\an1}No, not ninjutsu, but
ninshu... the Ninja Creed
that I had meant to be

178
00:14:56,095 --> 00:14:58,231
{\an1}something that gave birth to
hope.

179
00:14:58,265 --> 00:15:02,504
{\an1}Do not confuse it with
ninjutsu, which just breeds
conflict.

180
00:15:02,538 --> 00:15:07,310
{\an4}Oh, well, in any case, if
you're the Sage, I've
got tons of things that
I wanna ask you.

181
00:15:07,343 --> 00:15:09,914
{\an1}<i>But first, right now...</i>

182
00:15:17,257 --> 00:15:18,525
Huh?

183
00:15:21,629 --> 00:15:24,533
<i>You are my son,</i>
<i>Ashura's.</i>

184
00:15:27,637 --> 00:15:32,109
{\an1}In any event, right now a
lot of conditions have lined
up...

185
00:15:32,144 --> 00:15:35,181
{\an1}There are things that I must
entrust you with.

186
00:15:36,416 --> 00:15:39,119
{\an1}What is all this? Ashura?
Entrust me?

187
00:15:39,153 --> 00:15:43,892
{\an1}Look, no offense, but quit
spouting nonsense and let me
get out of here, all right?!

188
00:15:43,925 --> 00:15:48,265
I apologize, but
unfortunately that's not
something that I can affect.

189
00:15:48,298 --> 00:15:51,202
{\an1}That all depends on the
actions of those outside.

190
00:15:51,236 --> 00:15:54,206
{\an1}For now, I can only
relay things to you.

191
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:58,778
{\an1}We're back to this? You're
starting to lose me again
here, Gramps.

192
00:15:58,812 --> 00:16:03,385
{\an1}It means that right now...
trying to rush won't make
any difference.

193
00:16:03,418 --> 00:16:09,093
{\an1}So, I'd like you to listen
to me. No! You must hear
this.

194
00:16:09,494 --> 00:16:13,633
{\an1}First, I'll tell you about
my mother and my sons.

195
00:16:19,841 --> 00:16:26,049
{\an1}<i>My mother, Kaguya Otsutsuki,</i>
<i>came to this land of yours</i>
<i>from a faraway place in</i>

