00:16:26,082 --> 00:16:29,487
{\an1}<i>order to claim the fruit of</i>
<i>the Divine Tree. </i>

197
00:16:29,521 --> 00:16:34,527
{\an1}<i>The chakra fruit of that</i>
<i>same Divine Tree that you</i>
<i>have seen in this very war. </i>

